original_title: AIA President visits Port City Commission
original_body_lines: Asia Pacific’s biggest insurer AIA Global President Yuan Siong, Group President Tan Hak Leh, Regional CEO Leo Griffith, Regional CEO and Group Chief Strategy Officer Jayne Phunkett, Group Chief Risk and Compliance Officer CARA Ang, Group Chief HR Officer Kelvin Loh, Group Chief Healthcare Officer visited Port City Economic Commission Office last week for an overview of the Port City project. Port City Economic Commission Chairman and officials participated in the discussions.
